---
title: Mushroom Stroganoff with parsley rice
description: Stroganoff is a dish that has its origins in 19th Century Russia. As a recipe, Stroganoff is traditionally made with beef, however, veggie versions are often made with mushrooms due to their meaty texture. This mushroom Stroganoff comes with parsley rice and a helping of cooling creme fraiche.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W15_IE_IEVCLV14147-3_Main_high-8e819869.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/mushroom-stroganoff-6409db564091c75b27cc3954-607bfc44.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/mushroom-stroganoff-6409db564091c75b27cc3954
